rows.label: tlk43200141_03_msg0001
rows.name: Ion's cheered up a bit now, I'd say.

rows.label: tlk43200141_03_msg0002
rows.name:
She was giving herself a hard
time, 'cos she lost someone
close, and blamed herself for it.

rows.label: tlk43200141_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Nothing as bad as that has
ever happened to me, so it's
tough for me to understand.

rows.label: tlk43200141_03_msg0004
rows.name:
But, I still feel like I've
got to do everything I can
to help her to get over it.

rows.label: tlk43200141_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Eating loads of Fleur
Bavarian together seems
like a decent place to start.
